I"'<h1 class="no_toc" id="irida-dashboard-overview">IRIDA Dashboard Overview</h1>

<p>The IRIDA dashboard is the main location for accessing all of the data management and pipeline execution functionality built into IRIDA. This document describes the general features of the IRIDA dashboard.</p>

<ul id="markdown-toc">
  <li><a href="#main-dashboard" id="markdown-toc-main-dashboard">Main Dashboard</a></li>
  <li><a href="#main-menu" id="markdown-toc-main-menu">Main Menu</a>    <ul>
      <li><a href="#projects" id="markdown-toc-projects">Projects</a></li>
      <li><a href="#analyses" id="markdown-toc-analyses">Analyses</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><a href="#search" id="markdown-toc-search">Search</a></li>
  <li><a href="#cart" id="markdown-toc-cart">Cart</a></li>
  <li><a href="#settings" id="markdown-toc-settings">Settings</a>    <ul>
      <li><a href="#groups" id="markdown-toc-groups">Groups</a></li>
      <li><a href="#remote-instances-of-irida" id="markdown-toc-remote-instances-of-irida">Remote instances of IRIDA</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><a href="#user-settings" id="markdown-toc-user-settings">User Settings</a>    <ul>
      <li><a href="#logout" id="markdown-toc-logout">Logout</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><a href="#recent-activities" id="markdown-toc-recent-activities">Recent Activities</a></li>
